        qc (QuantumCircuit): Circuit to apply gates to
        a  (int)           : Alice's psi qubit (q0)
        b  (int)           : Alice's Bell qubit (q1)
        c  (int)           : Bob's qubit (q2)
    """
    qc.cx(b, c) # Controlled-X: b controls c
    qc.cz(a, c) # Controlled-Z: a controls c

